snippet.title: AbirReact
snippet.description:
Hello guys, It's Abir Ahmed Pias and this is my channel. I usually react to content such as movies and anime. I also do movie clips reaction and movie review as well. 

Almost all my videos are blind reaction and raw in format. There's little to no scripting going on, to keep my analyses as real as possible to my viewers.

Please subscribe and click the bell icon to get notified of all my videos. I try to upload as soon as the source materials are available, so please be patient with my upload time.
